title: Bug 121687: Exception throws when exporting data in a table inside a grid cell.
OB: When attempting to export data in a table inside a grid cell, an exception is thrown.
EB: Exporting data in a table inside a grid cell should not throw an exception.
SR: To reproduce the issue: 1. Insert a grid. 2. Insert a table into one grid cell. 3. Insert another table into another grid cell. 4. Attempt to export the data from the tables.
